{"tid":190335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《人民日報》：港警福利引人豔羨 收入豐厚","createTime":"2017-04-07T05:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T05:28:06.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5feadd962a22a0ba06940bef77b74cb67ea6df67","tid":190335,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:09:29.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，等睇一車車支那人投考黑警！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共喉舌《人民日報》昨再為「七犯」護航，指他們「辛苦執勤、每天平均工作15小時、承受巨大壓力&hellip;&hellip;卻遭重判入獄」，並以3,000字報道唱好港警，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當中提到他們人工高、福利好，「雖然工作辛苦，經常受點委屈」，但福利「也著實引人豔羨」，又訪問年輕警隊中人，指「相比於香港那些『社會主流』行業，可能只有當員警，會同時帶來豐厚收入和人生價值吧」。"},{"pid":"3a4c5e398c32448e4a8ac81bc72adeb7ffc48eed","tid":190335,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491540503_69c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491540503_69c6.jpg&h=691e1aec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9500925286d4871e821e06dde6dceac7bf01d2e8","tid":190335,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170407/large/1491540395_5ef4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170407%2Flarge%2F1491540395_5ef4.png&h=0ab2a468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70afca70373d058c787b905e20ff729326c2de9d","tid":190335,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"你地班廢青大撚鑊啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過多幾年班雙非、單非、新移民、支那童個撚個做晒黑警。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地班廢青女既x，男既y。"},{"pid":"e49635d4c59276fa6dcf5ad6a90902fdec04a301","tid":190335,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla